<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>订单确认通知</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.order-details {
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				padding: 15px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.item-list {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
			}
			.item {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				padding: 8px 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.total {
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-top: 15px;
				text-align: right;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>订单确认通知</h1>
		<p>尊敬的
			{{ order.customerName }}
			您好，</p>
		<p>感谢您的订购。您的订单已确认，订单号为：#{{ order.id }}</p>

		<div class="order-details">
			<h2>订单详情：</h2>
			<div class="item-list">
				{% for item in order.orderItems %}
					<div class="item">
						<span>{{ item.product.name }}
							x
							{{ item.quantity }}</span>
						<span>€{{ item.getSubtotal() }}</span>
					</div>
				{% endfor %}
			</div>
			<div class="total">
				总金额：€{{ order.totalAmount }}
			</div>
		</div>

		<p>取货信息：</p>
		<ul>
			<li>取货时间：{{ order.pickupTime|date('Y-m-d H:i') }}</li>
			<li>取货地点：{{ order.pickupLocation.name }}</li>
		</ul>

		<p>如有任何问题，请联系我们：{{ adminEmail }}</p>
	</body>
</html>
